> I thought i had done this 8*(
No, you provided a patch against stock linux-2.2.0-pre9 (as you
said). What it easier for me is a patch against stock
linux-2.2.0pre9+devfs-patch-v86.
> > > @@ -1067,8 +1079,9 @@
